# Contributing

Thanks for contributing to **AU Material Storage (AUMS)**.

This project is a GW2 API-powered Electron app intended for **read-only account/character browsing** (materials, inventory, etc.). Keep it safe, keep it legal, keep it focused. 


---

## Rules

1) **No private data.**
   - Never commit API keys, tokens, emails, account IDs, character names tied to personal info, or logs containing sensitive info.
   - If you need sample payloads, redact them.

2) **No automation / scraping / injection.**
   - No gameplay automation, input simulation, memory reads/writes, packet capture, overlay injection, or anything that could violate ArenaNet/NCSOFT terms.
   - This repo is for **official API consumption** only. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}

3) **Keep changes focused.**
   - One PR = one feature/fix/patch set.
   - Don’t mix UI styling, refactors, and new endpoints in one PR. :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}

4) **Preserve commentary + intentional “redundant” code.**
   - Do not delete existing comments/humor/“graveyard” code unless the maintainer explicitly asks.
   - If you must remove something for correctness, make it explicit and explain why.

5) **Patch-style edits preferred.**
   - When practical, submit changes as targeted diffs (small, readable edits) rather than wholesale file rewrites.

---

## Development Setup

### Requirements
- Node.js + npm
- Windows recommended (GW2 ecosystem reality)

### Install
```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd AU-Material-Storage
npm install
